              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-401D14W2-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">SEVERAL OF THEM WRITTEN IN 1726.&#13;</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-401D14W2-headnote-2">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-401D14W2-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-401D14W2-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1">I. ON A WINDOW AT AN INN.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-401D14W2-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-401D14W2-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-401D14W2-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-401D14W2-line-1" n="1">W<hi rend="small-caps">E</hi> fly from luxury and wealth,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D14W2-line-2" n="2">To hardships, in pursuit of health;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D14W2-line-3" n="3">From generous wines, and costly fare,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D14W2-line-4" n="4">And dozing in an easy-chair;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D14W2-line-5" n="5">Pursue the goddess Health in vain,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D14W2-line-6" n="6">To find her in a country scene,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D14W2-line-7" n="7">And everywhere her footsteps trace,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D14W2-line-8" n="8">And see her marks in every face;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D14W2-line-9" n="9">And still her favourites we meet,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D14W2-line-10" n="10">Crowding the roads with naked feet.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D14W2-line-11" n="11">But, oh! so faintly we pursue,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-401D14W2-line-12" n="12">We ne'er can have her full in view.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
